{"word":"G2704 - καταφθείρω - kataphtheírō - kat-af-thi'-ro - Corrupt","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταφθείρω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kataphtheírō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-af-thi'-ro</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Corrupt</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - துர்ப்புத்தியாயிரு, கெட்டழி"},{"paragraph":"1. to corrupt, deprave"},{"paragraph":"2. to destroy; to be destroyed, to perish"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G5351 - φθείρω - phtheírō - fthi'-ro/5351\">G5351</a>; to <i>spoil entirely</i>, that is, (literally) to <i>destroy</i>; or (figuratively) to <i>deprave:</i> - corrupt, utterly perish.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1311/1311\">G1311</a>, <a href=\"#/G1312/1312\">G1312</a>, <a href=\"#/G2704/2704\">G2704</a>, <a href=\"#/G5256/5256\">G5256</a>, <a href=\"#/G5349/5349\">G5349</a>, <a href=\"#/G5351/5351\">G5351</a>, <a href=\"#/G861/861\">G861</a>, <a href=\"#/G862/862\">G862</a>, <a href=\"#/G90/90\">G90</a>"}]}